## üöÄ Quick Start
For once, this is going to be painless ü§ó.

### Installation

With `uv`:
```bash
uv add tinyros
```
With `pip`:
```bash
pip install tinyros
```

For the installation from source or for development, please see our [Contributing Guide](./CONTRIBUTING.md).

